				<div id="mw-content-text" lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr"><div class="dablink">For other senses of the term, see <a href="Roman_Empire_(disambiguation)" title="Roman Empire (disambiguation)">Roman Empire (disambiguation)</a>. "Imperium Romanum" redirects here. For the video game, see <a href="Imperium_Romanum_(video_game)" title="Imperium Romanum (video game)">Imperium Romanum (video game)</a>.</div>
