<li><a href="Constantinople" title="Constantinople">Constantinople</a> from 330, with a Western counterpart in <a href="Mediolanum" title="Mediolanum">Milan</a> and later <a href="Ravenna" title="Ravenna">Ravenna</a><sup id="cite_ref-Constantine_I_306_-_337_AD_3-0" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-Constantine_I_306_-_337_AD-3"><span>[</span>3<span>]</span></a></sup></li>
